{
  "stem": "20021.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I did that and I missed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's enough you miss one-- the key didn't fit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She comes the next thing to the place and she had such a leather-- every German was walking with such a leather strip-- strap.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she straps with it, hits me over-- straight over my face and throws the key and tells me, you better make that key fit or else you will pay with you life.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So of course, I was helped at that point and double checked that the key should fit and all that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But then at lunchtime, I sat down and with one of the guys-- a plain, very plain spoken person, you know, who still worked for my father from years before.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We sat down there and talked to each other and he tells me, I would not put up with something like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I left and I thought, [INAUDIBLE] so what will you do?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he said, I would run into the forest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, how will you live in the forest and so forth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we got to talking, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And suddenly, the fact that she hit me like that and what he was kept telling me-- and in the process of this conversation, he also told me that in his village there is a man by the name of [INAUDIBLE], who went in 1939 to the war and never came back.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And his mother doesn't know till today what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There is no letter, no word, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I asked him, could you go to the priest and somehow ask him for a birth certificate?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said, yes, he could go to the priest and ask for a birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
